{"tid":442560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾聲援佔中　台教授申來港簽證遭拒　未悉原因","createTime":"2017-10-20T17:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T10:38:30.000Z","uid":43189,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0af65abae93fea6e55a63a4bb9d7c296867bc113","tid":442560,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"關注社會議題、以社會現象為創作素材的台灣「生祥樂隊」，昨日於香港中文大學舉行「圍庄香港演唱會」。台灣人權促進會執委、國立屏東大學社會發展學系助理教授邱毓斌昨晚於Facebook上表示，由於早前申請的「香港旅遊入境許可證」（即「港簽」）遭拒，無法參與該演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n邱毓斌過往一直積極參與台灣的社會運動，此外還曾聲援2014年香港的雨傘運動，2014年底在台灣參與〈從雨傘運動看香港政治與社會發展〉等專題講座，曾喊出「今日香港，今日台灣」的口號，希望兩邊同時努力，並為香港民眾打氣：「香港，你不孤單！」<br />\n<br />\n他昨晚在Facebook指，過去20年因為工會、研究、工作的關係，頻繁造訪香港，幾乎把香港當成第二故鄉。他又說，「對油麻地大街小巷的熟悉，大概就僅次於我長大的高雄灣子內。」<br />\n<br />\n「有點憤怒，有點傷心。就像你一堆寶貴的檔案，突然被鎖在掛掉的硬碟裡。剩下記憶。為了旺角街市裡道地的燒味，為了茶餐廳裡的凍奶茶，一定盡全力早日把這硬碟撬開搞定。」<br />\n<br />\n持有有效《台灣居民來往大陸通行證》（即「台胞證」）的台灣居民，無須申請港簽便能訪港。但邱毓斌在Facebook回應網友指，「台胞證早過期了。我都只到香港，沒有要進去中國」。他笑說「我的目的從來就真的是去燒臘店啊」，又笑言「要給香港政府一個重新做人的機會」。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》向入境處查詢這宗拒入境事宜，暫未獲覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%9B%BE%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD-%E5%8F%B0%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E7%94%B3%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E6%9C%AA%E6%82%89%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0/#.WeimhIOH0nQ.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2582%2589%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0%2F%23.WeimhIOH0nQ.facebook&d=HvnfUf5OLwwsvTyJ8D7oab%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c207f2b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2582%2589%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0%2F%23.WeimhIOH0nQ.facebook&h=4171fa4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%9B%BE%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD-%E5%8F%B0%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E7%94%B3%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E6%9C%AA%E6%82%89%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0/#.WeimhIOH0nQ.facebook</a>"},{"pid":"952162c5d2c36d770afb2ad73076aff73f7deb36","tid":442560,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"英美德法日意俄奧"},{"pid":"c01c2c6f4e23eb3a4e83ade3c754c42155f6beac","tid":442560,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:48:54.000Z","msg":"淋病回應下"},{"pid":"5e9c73e879d4814de4db5e2b1e0b694491b87f78","tid":442560,"uid":39796,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:44:02.000Z","msg":"入境處開始同黑警一擔擔"},{"pid":"b8bac90c6395f1200cb77c423fb0185b1f4a56c5","tid":442560,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:46:33.000Z","msg":"我正式宣佈林鄭已被架空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa273d776e3fd7302d468aa83734697ec5876822","tid":442560,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:48:46.000Z","msg":"咁快學埋澳門啲衰嘢"},{"pid":"9b9dd3075dc7bf26b9e747055700131646999a33","tid":442560,"uid":13173,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T22:28:14.000Z","msg":"開始鎖港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5404641ac2c53347cbf1c38dd8980f875daedf0f","tid":442560,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:47:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"df39d199a7c981e9ac0e6e53d42e3c330424ee18","tid":442560,"uid":132038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:45:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c8dea23e6762d3f7bf4a347cfd386aa60caf991","tid":442560,